org.pcc.pams.objects

Class Fan

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pcc.pams.objects.PhysicsObject
      • org.pcc.pams.objects.Fan

  • public class Fan
extends PhysicsObject
    Represents a fan. The fan is located in a point of the screen and blows air in a cone area in front of it, pushing bubbles away.

      • getConeCoordinates

        public int[][] getConeCoordinates(double length)

        Parameters:
        length - The length to impose on the cone's sides' vectors.
        Returns:
        The x and y coordinates of the wind cone's points.
